Title: Realtime Checks: fixed race condition which caused loss of counter data
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.4.0p28
Date: 1521640214
Class: fix

If a host got data from realtime checks, as well as the regular check, there was a risk of loosing counter data.
Missing counter data generally leads to stale services. This has been fixed.
